{"tid":1865051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[老人與貓派貨啦] 網購口罩集運討論2","createTime":"2020-02-06T03:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T12:41:57.000Z","uid":3233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4236835a554d9b9cc0c4506265d2259315c4c965","tid":1865051,"uid":3233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:18:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。投資者在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon自己送<br />\nKatolec=老人<br />\nYamato=貓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsq6yyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsq6yyZ.jpg&h=8752b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04670c1f97fd79f1020e55a7b70b2e65a9473b7e","tid":1865051,"uid":97710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbd3f4e8a9f4565c42f1323b5e2fc1de9f179c4","tid":1865051,"uid":2341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:19:50.000Z","msg":"[member]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/member"},{"pid":"6e5b950f90831bfd4c230fd475e93e95b018dc15","tid":1865051,"uid":3233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r